  "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EWe take pride in our efficient and effective operations as well as the reliability of our employees. Consistent, punctual attendance is critical to meeting business objectives, ensuring smooth operations, and providing excellent service to our clients. You are expected to report to work on time for all scheduled shifts and to notify your manager in advance of any absence or delay. Any and all changes to scheduled work days or hours must be discussed with and approved by your manager in advance. Unplanned absences or excessive lateness can disrupt teamwork and impact productivity, and will be addressed in accordance with our progressive discipline policy.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E"
}]]></Value>
